::Nightlight/Windlord::

"Where's Trinity?" said worried Nightlight

"Aerotaur went to finde her" aanwered Windlord trying to calm her down

"She and her new friend could be in danger... We must find her!!!!" 
said Nightlight

"You need rest!!! " anwered Windlord trying to stop her.

"I'll find them" she said an ran in beast mode towards the same road 
that Aerotaur had took.

"No wait....!!!!" screamed Windlord but she had lost "Great!!!!"

Windlord tranformed and took off in order to do a air-search
